      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint protected by a professional ceramic coating, the exterior is absolutely flawless\u2014free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the original factory-spec floor mats are untouched. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships and kept in a climate-controlled garage its entire life. The undercarriage is as clean as the body, with no signs of leaks, rust, or road grime. This is a turn-key masterpiece for the discerning enthusiast who demands a showroom-fresh experience.",
